  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trapped in what seems to be an endless hospital department. Carefully observe your surroundings in each loop to escape the Liminal Department</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Phenomenon Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an ever-changing hallway filled with unusual occurrences. Each loop could have multiple anomalies or none. Some are easy to spot, others are not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/d73ac64f14f813ac458f1d6cef625a98.poster.avif?t=1765189406\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/d73ac64f14f813ac458f1d6cef625a98.webm?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/d73ac64f14f813ac458f1d6cef625a98.mp4?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VHS Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS tape style mode with zooming feature. Experience a nostalgic liminal feel with the old classic camera interface and visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/faa28b3d6918ea2d9263106a394d7097.poster.avif?t=1765189406\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/faa28b3d6918ea2d9263106a394d7097.webm?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/faa28b3d6918ea2d9263106a394d7097.mp4?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Submit for Anomalies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a careful examination submit for anomalies to proceed further. Memory skills are key to breaking the loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/5e7d83025666fa1a884aa83a2e196443.poster.avif?t=1765189406\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/5e7d83025666fa1a884aa83a2e196443.webm?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/5e7d83025666fa1a884aa83a2e196443.mp4?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trapped In a Loop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caught in a never-ending loop, leaving the department only leads you right back into the same hallway. Reach department 13 to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/fd9f67b39c5e3d38e346fe6587cf8963.poster.avif?t=1765189406\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/fd9f67b39c5e3d38e346fe6587cf8963.webm?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3412000/extras/fd9f67b39c5e3d38e346fe6587cf8963.mp4?t=1765189406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic and eerie experience with minimal UI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS mode with zooming feature</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 60 anomalies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera bobbing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li></ul>",
